properties.Name: Union Station
properties.hours: Monday through Thursday, 9:00a to 7:00pm; Friday, 9:00am to 5:30pm; first and fourth Saturday of the month, 9:00am to 3:00pm.
properties.description: Union Station is a major transportation hub in the County of Los Angeles.  It includes Amtrak, Metrolink, and Metro Red Line and Gold Line stops. There are 1,162 parking spots at the station, nearby Paid Parking (Independent)  Union Station - 8 Bike Rack Spaces Gateway - 16 Bike Rack Spaces/32 Bike Lockers
